                    <MudImage Src="images/mony.jpg" Alt="An image of the best dog ever!"></MudImage>
                </MudAvatar>
                <br/><br/>
                <MudText Typo="Typo.h6"><b>Victor Nwogu.</b></MudText>
                <MudText Typo="Typo.body2"><b>Event Organizer.</b></MudText>
                <br/>
                <div id="testimonies-description">
                    Managing multiple events used to be a headache, but IVS changed everything. From tracking ticket sales to real-time analytics, we’ve gained total control and confidence in our event planning.
                    </div>
            </MudItem>

            <MudItem xs="12" sm="12" md="12" lg="4" xl="4" xxl="4">
                <MudAvatar Style="height:150px; width:150px;">
                    <MudImage Src="images/mony.jpg" Alt="An image of the best dog ever!"></MudImage>
                </MudAvatar>
                <br/><br/>
                <MudText Typo="Typo.h6"><b>Victor Nwogu.</b></MudText>
                <MudText Typo="Typo.body2"><b>Event Organizer.</b></MudText>
                <br/>
                <div id="testimonies-description">
                    Buying tickets through IVS was quick and easy. The platform is user-friendly, and I loved that I could pay securely in seconds.
                    </div>
            </MudItem>
        </MudGrid>

    </div>
    
